.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
4 different games are played: canasta, billiard, go, scrabble
House: victorian, futuristic, farmhouse, ranch-style
1. the farmhouse house is on the right of the futuristic house##1
2. the person playing scrabble is the farmhouse house##1
3. the person playing scrabble is on the far right##1
4. the person playing billiard is the victorian house##1
5. the person playing go is between the person playing canasta and the person playing billiard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Game   | billiard     | go           | canasta | scrabble  |
| House         | victorian | ranch-style | futuristic   | farmhouse |

