.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
There 4 different types of food: kale, pomegranate, pear, eggplant
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, marigold, iris, dahlia
1. the person eating pomegranate is the person who growsaconite##1
2. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
3. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person eating kale##1
4. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
5. the person eating kale is between the person who growsaconite and the person eating pear##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Food   | eggplant   | pomegranate | kale | pear      |
| Flower     | iris | aconite    | marigold  | dahlia |

