.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
4 different pets are kept: rat, hamster, chinchilla, turtle
House: townhouse, gothic-revival, ranch-style, cape-cod
1. the townhouse house is the owner of the hamster##1
2. the gothic-revival house is between the owner of the chinchilla and the ranch-style house##2
3. the owner of the rat is on the far left##1
4. the townhouse house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Pet       | rat | turtle | chinchilla     | hamster   |
| House   | ranch-style   | gothic-revival     | cape-cod | townhouse |

