.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, july, march, october
4 different pets are kept: fish, horse, rat, rabbit
1. the person who's birthday is in march is between the owner of the fish and the person who's birthday is in august##2
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
4. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Birthday         | july | march | august | october |
| Pet   | fish         | rabbit       | horse    | rat         |

