.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, juice, sprite
City: paris, nizza, berlin, liverpool
1. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
5. the person traveling to nizza is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person traveling to liverpool##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage    | sprite   | juice      | iced-tea   | 7up  |
| City   | liverpool | nizza | berlin | paris |

