.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
4 different games are played: chess, backgammon, whist, domino
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, indie, soul, blues
1. the fan blues is on the right of the fan indie##1
2. the person playing backgammon is between the person playing domino and the person playing chess##2
3. the fan indie is on the right of the fan soul##1
4. the fan soul is on the right of the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Game          | chess     | backgammon | domino   | whist        |
| Music-Genre   | trance | soul   | indie | blues |

