.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, cain, pall-mall, chaman
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, almond-milk, milk, water
1. the person drinking milk is the cain-smoker##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking water##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is the ritmeester-smoker##1
4. the pall-mall-smoker is the person drinking almond-milk##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
6. the person drinking almond-milk is between the cain-smoker and the chaman-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Cigar         | cain | pall-mall | chaman | ritmeester |
| Beverage   | milk          | almond-milk     | water  | lemonade     |

