.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-16::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, balloon-flower, rose, sunflower
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, may, february, december
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person who growssunflower is the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person who growsrose is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person who growsballoon-flower##2
4. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |
| Flower   | bellflower | balloon-flower | rose | sunflower |
| Birthday     | october     | may   | december | february  |

