.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, roller, subway, scooter
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, videographer, musician, journalist
1. the videographer is on the left of the journalist##1
2. the designer is on the left of the videographer##1
3. the person driving the scooter is the designer##1
4. the journalist is between the person driving the motorbike and the person driving the subway##2
5. the person driving the subway is the musician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Transport   | scooter   | motorbike   | roller | subway |
| Job         | designer | videographer | journalist     | musician    |

