2. the colonial house is between the person who growsorchid and the modern house##2
3. the modern house is on the left of the colonial house##1
4. the victorian house is on the far right##1
5. the victorian house is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| House   | ranch-style    | modern     | colonial | victorian |
| Flower     | zinnia | bellflower | marigold       | orchid     |

 